        "## Kriging: Modeling Basics\n",
        "\n",
        "### The Kriging Idea in a Nutshell\n",
        "\n",
        "We consider observed data of an unknown function $f$ at $n$ points $x_1, \\ldots, x_n$, see @fig-unknownf.\n",
