      "source": [
        "#### The Objective Function\n",
        "\n",
        "* Here we use $\\sum_{i=1}^n (x_i-1)^2$.\n",
        "* `f_map()` is a helper function that maps $f$ to the entries (points) in the matrix $X$.\n"
